This program intend to cover the usage of [TCP/UDP] [server/client] [sync/async] 
using boost library.

This program based on the formal boost documentation.
boost/asio library based on io_service, which is the main api,
one passed to a thread the io_service most be run in order to be executed.
it is wrapping a dedicated scheduler responsible for the sync/async behaviour,
socket setting socket option binding is not direct and wrapped with UDP or TCP dedicated API's.
